summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department, accepting NINE easements for watermain purposes, THREE easements for fire hydrant purposes, and ONE easement for water meter purposes over portion of: Bradners Garden Tracts; T. Hanford's Addition; Hillman City Addition; C.D. Hillman's Meadow Garden Addition, Division No. 2; Section 31, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; Section 25, Township 26 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; Sommerville; Gilman's Addition; Seattle Tide Lands in Section 23, Township 25 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; Section 33, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; Section 11, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; and Chittenden's Terrace Park Addition all in King County, Washington (Private Contracts.)
